Effectiveness of a phone-based nurse monitoring assessment and intervention for 
chemotherapy-related toxicity: A randomized multicenter trial.

Antonuzzo A(1), Ripamonti CI(2), Roila F(3), Sbrana A(4), Galli L(1), Miccinesi 
G(5), Sammarco E(1), Berruti A(6), Coletta D(7), Velutti L(8), Fabi A(9), Corsi 
